data.value: The output will activate when the triggering conditions are satisfied and remain activated for a specific pre-defined length of time. If the input conditions activate again before the output de-activates, the activation time will be extended, essentially re-triggering the output for the pre-defined length of time.

data.name: GalaxyOutputMode_Timeout_Description
